subject: Nordic Combined (Winter Sport Event)
Olympic Games
lead_paragraph: Johnny Spillane of the United States earned his first Nordic combined World Cup victory on Sunday in Oberhof, Germany, beating Felix Gottwald of Austria by more than 30 seconds.
